<div1 type="summary">
<p>Inviting Austin to conference</p>
</div1>

<div1 type="body">

<p><location_mentioned>Velasco </location_mentioned><date_mentioned n="07-04-1836">4 July 1836</date_mentioned></p>

<p>My Dear Sir</p>

<p>Your note by <person_mentioned>Judge Tennel</person_mentioned> was recd <date_mentioned n="07-03-1836">last evening</date_mentioned>— I hope Soon to See
You here Soon— The Yellow Stone has got into <location_mentioned>Galveston </location_mentioned>Particulars
not heard—</p>

<p>Expecting You Soon I shall make no remarks on public matters—</p>
<p><person_mentioned>D G Burnet</person_mentioned></p>

<p>[Addressed:] <person_mentioned>Genl S. F. Austin</person_mentioned> at <location_mentioned><person_mentioned>Mr Perry</person_mentioned>'s</location_mentioned></p>


</div1>
